Sentencas: In SmBa1-xCaxCo2O5+d (x = 0.01, 0.03, 0.1, and 0.2, SBCCO) oxide systems calcined at 1100 degrees C for 8 h, the XRD patterns of the SBCCO single phase were maintained in the cases of SmBa0.97Ca0.03Co2O5+d (SBCCO-0.97) and SmBa0.99Ca0.01Co2O5+d (SBCCO-0.99) compositions.
Titulo: SmBa1-xCaxCo2O5+d Layered Perovskite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature-operating Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: In SmBa0.8Ca0.2Co2O5+d (SBCCO-0.8) and SmBa0.9Ca0.1Co2O5+d (SBCCO-0.9), CaCoSmO4 existed with the pattern SBCCO.
Titulo: SmBa1-xCaxCo2O5+d Layered Perovskite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature-operating Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: SBCCO structures were identified as orthorhombic crystal structures because they showed splitting of the X-ray diffraction (XRD) peaks at 23.4 degrees, 47.9 degrees, and 59.1 degrees.
Titulo: SmBa1-xCaxCo2O5+d Layered Perovskite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature-operating Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Typical metallic conduction behaviors were found in all measured compositions except SBCCO-0.8, which showed a metal-insulator transition (MIT) behavior.
Titulo: SmBa1-xCaxCo2O5+d Layered Perovskite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature-operating Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Compared to other SmBa1-xCaxCo2O5+d compositions, SBCCO-0.8 showed the highest electrical conductivity of 460 S/cm at 500 degrees C.
Titulo: SmBa1-xCaxCo2O5+d Layered Perovskite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature-operating Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: In particular, SBCCO-0.9 was found to have an excellent ASR characteristic of about 0.077 omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: SmBa1-xCaxCo2O5+d Layered Perovskite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature-operating Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The activation energy of SBCCO-0.9 was the lowest among SBCCO oxide systems with a value of 0.77 eV.
Titulo: SmBa1-xCaxCo2O5+d Layered Perovskite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature-operating Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
